# Industrial Applications

## Overview

Industrial applications require thick polyester films because of their excellent dielectric strength, thermal stability, chemical resistance, and dimensional accuracy. These films are used in high-performance engineering applications where durability is critical.

---

## Market Analysis

- Represents approximately 20–25% of specialty polyester film consumption.

- Demand is increasing due to electrification, renewable energy, electronics manufacturing, and EV adoption.

- Industrial-grade PET films typically command higher margins than commodity packaging films.

